{"tid":1492981,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"BNO係英國人？俾個機會你地等英國佬正式話你唔係英國人","createTime":"2019-08-21T05:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T13:35:28.000Z","uid":294632,"like":2,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3ffc6ac3a254003ce7eb945f24afc68b95ccd61b","tid":1492981,"uid":294632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41PDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=81bc70d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n係人都知班英國佬一直都收緊中國利益就係人都知<br />\n你班BNO撚咁自私 割我地 你睇真d個petition 寫咩？成班傻仔 講真入便有幾多冇bc bno都簽 成份假野 <br />\n你地咁想做英國人 今日開始我地就簽夠10萬等你班賣國賊開心<br />\n我相信英國佬實會玩鳩你班偽英國人 大大聲話你BNO冇份呀屌你老母 直接取消BNO <br />\n請分享<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce85968dd4621730013c0ba3016727a805706a3","tid":1492981,"uid":94312,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gV614ud.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgV614ud.jpg&h=88bc743c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1456f6954b56d945159478dc8ed601ce3f34cd3","tid":1492981,"uid":67444,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:19:24.000Z","msg":"P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由得個post沉"},{"pid":"f57e655c28b17aaa017bcd9393510605051b2b0b","tid":1492981,"uid":228955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:19:50.000Z","msg":"而家香港已經變成一個奶共既垃圾地方落去只有越嚟越差所以乜嘢有機會都要試吓"},{"pid":"9cc03d5dbb440e3a0c2339019cad43db573f6093","tid":1492981,"uid":94312,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"rep